      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.cQtmz297P5g6g5xv]{Advanced Mods}</p>\n<p>Your drone is equipped with a thin coating that can change color to match the drone’s surroundings. Whenever your drone stays stationary for 1 round, it gains a +10 bonus to Stealth checks (this bonus doesn’t stack with the <em>@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.Item.YDXegEus8p0BnsH1]{Invisibility}</em> spell or similar effects). If your drone takes any action, it loses this bonus until it once again spends 1 round remaining still.</p>"
